title: Complete the Square
text: Group and factor: (x**2 + 2x) + 100(y**2 - 10y) $$=$$ $$-2401$$. Then complete the square.

title: Divide to Get Standard Form
text: After completing the square: $$\frac{\left(x+1\right)^2}{49}$$ + $$\frac{\left(y-5\right)^2}{16}$$ $$=$$ $$1$$. Identify a $$=$$ $$7$$, $$b$$ $$=$$ $$4$$.
